t-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1166em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 表示 action <span v-pre class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6595em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">i</span></span></span></span> 被 sample 到的機率</li>
